### ğŸ§  Project Focus
The project analyzes **global trade inequality** using international trade data, with an emphasis on:

- Exploratory analysis of large-scale economic data
- Distributional and inequality patterns across countries and regions
- Group-wise and comparative statistical analysis
- Translating complex trade data into interpretable insights

The Jupyter notebook contains the **full analytical workflow**, while the PDF files correspond to **formal milestone submissions and written reports**.

